<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shellfish Insurance Quoter</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">

</head>
<body>
    <!-- Top Banner with Logo and Buttons -->
    <header>
        <div class="banner">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="/images/ranchersinsurancelogo.png" alt="Rancher's Insurance Logo">
            </div>
            <h1>Shellfish Insurance Quoter</h1>
            <div class="auth-buttons">
                <a href="/login" class="button">Log In</a>
                <a href="/guest" class="button">Continue as Guest</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content Area -->
    <main>
        <h1>Database Configuration</h1>
        <table border="1">
          <tr>
            <th>Key</th>
            <th>Value</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Hostname</td>
            <td><%= dbConfig.hostname %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Username</td>
            <td><%= dbConfig.username %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Password</td>
            <td><%= dbConfig.password %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Database Name</td>
            <td><%= dbConfig.dbName %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Port</td>
            <td><%= dbConfig.port %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>SSL</td>
            <td><%= dbConfig.ssl %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="column" id="about-us">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>We are based in Northern Utah and serve farmers and ranchers nationwide. We provide policies and industry leading expertise and guidance in insuring Cattle, Crops, and now Shellfish. We are invested in helping you get the best possible plan to insure your livelihood!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="column" id="how-it-works">
                <h2>How This Tool Works</h2>
                <p>This tool is designed to estimate the commodity value of the current year's yield which can then be insured. This tool is primarily for creating estimations and getting a starting point when creating a policy for your farm. Click <b>Log In</b> above and make an account, or continue as guest if you don't want to save your information.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="footer-banner">
            &copy; Rancher's Insurance 2024
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>